{"tid":1108251,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人睇完一念無明覺得好黑暗釋懷唔到","createTime":"2019-04-15T23:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T06:38:13.000Z","uid":195396,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a3633ae185de23e3d264daa7014a0fda5c754be7","tid":1108251,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"養父母究竟係唔係我哋嘅責任<br />\n咁多人養父母係真係想佢哋好 定係純粹唔想畀人冠以不孝子嘅名<br />\n喺香港地點樣可以確保老人家有好嘅生活同照顧<br />\n一個老人家 見到自己變成負累 個心會係點諗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0995652de32d35738c29adbe48d8837054d245e4","tid":1108251,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18113143944703d7d6cb82d481017e30d72e46a5","tid":1108251,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1208ba6754975e2b0fd3f2fe10f12e9a52d263c","tid":1108251,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n我阿媽行動不便，但我因為各種家庭問題，自己搬走左好多年<br />\n有啲咩事應該都係我細佬負責"},{"pid":"c82925fd244ed70b69e11589ca32eb9836349621","tid":1108251,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaa97662f65f97aad72e913ec2f6f937762ddfd","tid":1108251,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1208ba6754975e2b0fd3f2fe10f12e9a52d263c","tid":1108251,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019